               <title value="Hospital course note"/>
               <code>
                  <coding>
                     <system value="http://loinc.org"/>
                     <code value="8648-8"/>
                     <display value="Hospital course note"/>
                  </coding>
               </code>
               <text>
                  <status value="generated"/>
                  <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Dear colleague, I am writing to inform you regarding the discharge of your 56-year-old male patient admitted on 13.12.2012 for evaluation of sleep disorder. During his brief inpatient stay, we conducted a comprehensive sleep assessment including detailed sleep history, Epworth Sleepiness Scale scoring, and overnight polysomnography to objectively characterize his sleep disturbance. Investigations revealed findings consistent with unspecified sleep disorder (ICD-10: G47.9), without evidence of significant obstructive sleep apnoea requiring immediate intervention. We initiated sleep hygiene counselling and provided structured relaxation guidance. A short-term low-dose pharmacological support was prescribed to stabilize sleep pattern. We recommend outpatient follow-up with sleep specialist review of polysomnography results. Please find enclosed the full investigation reports. Should you have any queries, do not hesitate to contact our department directly.</div>
               </text>
            </section>
